BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:siNklaWhxRlHKcl9EWWt4
SUMMARY:[NWMetal] NORTHWEST TERROR FEST – headlined by Kylesa\, Oranssi Paz
	uzu\, and Pig Destroyer\, with appearances by Black Breath\, Deadguy\, Wor
	m\, and many more.
DTSTAMP:20260401T021327Z
DTSTART:20260509T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:From NW Metal Calendar
